snippet.title: I made World’s Biggest Jolo Chips!🌶️🥵 *& ate it* 😭

snippet.title: Thalapathy Vijay’s Ultimate Mass Scenes from Theri! 🔥 | Atlee | Samantha | Sun NXT
snippet.description:
Relive the ultimate mass moments of Baby Joseph Kuruvilla in Theri! Watch Ilayathalapathy Vijay in action, directed by Atlee, alongside Samantha. Don’t miss the thrill and emotions packed in this blockbuster. Now streaming on Sun NXT!

#Theri #Vijay #nainika #theribaby #Sammantha #atlee #sunnxt #tamil #tamilhitmovie #thalapathyvijay  #Lovescenes #romanticproposal 

00:00 - Powerful Police Station Scene 🚔
02:04 - Epic Rain Fight 🌧️⚡
05:40 - Intense School Fight 🏫🥊
09:34 - High-Octane Road Fight 🚗🔥
13:10 - Theri Mass Reveal Moment 🔥
14:46 - Action-Packed Coffee Shop Fight ☕🥊
16:13 - Explosive Construction Site Battle 🚧💥

Theri  is a 2016 Indian Tamil-language action thriller film directed by Atlee and produced by Kalaipuli S. Thanu under the banner V Creations. Loosely inspired from the 1990 Tamil film Chatriyan and 2013 Hollywood film Homefront, the film stars Vijay, Samantha Ruth Prabhu, Amy Jackson, Nainika.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4334 | 1 Mar 2025 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4334: Kar Bhala To Hoga Bhala
--------------------------------------------------------
Joshi Kaka presents Sonu with potential matches, but she turns them all down. Meanwhile, Kanji Kaka does the same for Tapu. How will Tapu and Sonu handle this situation?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4334 | 28 Feb 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090470132

snippet.title: Get Ready For An Action-Packed Season!
snippet.description:
Buckle up, soldier! The villainous Minion General is striking across the land like a Lightning Spell. There's only one fighting force strong enough to stop him: the Action Heroes!

Clash of Clans "Action Heroes" Season starts March 1st 08:00AM UTC! 


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
https://supercell.com/en/parents/

#clashofclans #actionheroes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Badshah - Dear Aditya (Official Music Video) | Hiten
snippet.description:
A Letter To Myself

Audio Credits :
➟ Performed By Badshah
➟ Lyrics By Badshah
➟ Composed By  Badshah
➟ Music Produced By Hiten 
➟ Mixed & Mastered By Hiten
➟ Chorus Performed by Vaidik Dawale, Aanya Jain, Veda Mahajan & Advik Kasbe

Lyrics: 
Kaisa hai kya haal hai kya chal raha hai
Gaane vaane sun raha hai ya padh raha hai
Jitna marzi rishtedar tere peeche padein dekh
Dariyo na tu sapne dekh aur bade dekh
Ye jaankar tu aaj bada dang hoga
Ke pandran saal mein in sabka mooh band hoga
Jin teacheron ko tujhse zaraa bhi ummeed nai thi un saare teacheron ki naak mein dum

Papa ka thoda dhyaan rakh unka dil kamzor hai
Tere aas paas aadhe se zaada bande chor hain
Dost kam rakhiyo circle usse chota
Paisa boht aane wala hai wallet mota rakhiyo
Maa baap ke siva koi saga nai milega
Sukoon ghar ko chod kisi jagah nai milega
Jisko pyaar tu karega dil wo tera todegi
Kisi paise wale ke liye wo tujhe chodegi
Ek dedh hafta rona, man kare to chillana
Lekin fir chup chaap wapas music pe lag jaana
Uski yaad mein koi sad songs nahi banaiyo
Log waise hi boht rote hain tu party karaiyo

Koi dedh chaal chale to tu dhai samajhna
Par jo pakde tera hath use bhai samajhna
Par kain baar hath deke hathon ki lakeerein le jaate hain log tab hathon ki safai samajhna
Hateron ka dil dekh dehelte rahega
Shuru jaise marzi karaa ant keher se karega
2 kamron ke ghar mein tha janma tu tujhe pata nahi tu ek din kitne bade mahal mein rahega
Maa khush hogi lekin papa khush ni rahenge
Unka man hai tu IAS bane par push ni karenge
Log teri lagataar kaamyaabi dekh bore hoke hate karenge par mooh pe kuch ni kahenge

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Behkaave mein aake tu sidein switch nai karna
Fame ke chakkar mein kisiko diss nai karna
Khoob mehnat karna sirf wish nai karna
Aur jab saamne nishaana ho to miss nai karna
tujhe ladna hi hoga
Chahe kat jayen taangein aage badhna hi hog
Yaad rakh fame ek kiraaye ka makaan hai
Ek din tujhe ise khali karna hi hoga
jaam na sharaab lena, pyaar behisaab dena
Mooh kam kholiyo tu Kaam se jawaab dena
Banda tujhse kya chahe aankhon se bhaanp lena
Jo karega wo bharega khud ko na paap dena

Chaltre reh rukh nai
Khone ko kuch nai
Humko tujhe pe hai yakeen
Humko khudh pe hai yakeen
Rakhna mat tu sabr
Cheen le 
Kood kar 
Aasmaan aur Zameen 
Humko tujh pe hai yakeen

Haan…. tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga
Naam badshah aur sabko tera naam yaad hoga
Haan…. Tu itna zaada kaamyaab hoga

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for the greatest adventure ever built. ⛏️ Tickets are on sale NOW for #MinecraftMovie – only in theaters April 4. https://www.fandango.com/MinecraftMovie

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, “A Minecraft Movie,” directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time. 

The film also stars Emma Myers (“Wednesday”), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (“The Color Purple”), Sebastian Hansen (“Just Mercy, “Lisey’s Story”), with Jennifer Coolidge. 

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn’t just help you craft, it’s essential to one’s survival! Four misfits—Garrett “The Garbage Man” Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)—find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they’ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative…the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (“Ninety-Five Senses,” “Nacho Libre”) directed from a screenplay by Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer and Neil Widener & Gavin James and Chris Galletta, story by Allison Schroeder and Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, based on the Minecraft video game. Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Ólafsson and Vu Bui produced, and Todd Hallowell, Jay Ashenfelter, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza and Jon Spaihts executive produced. 

The director’s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (“127 Hours,” “Transformers: Rise of the Beasts”), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (“The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,” “The Meg”), editor James Thomas (“Pokémon: Detective Pikachu”, the “Borat” films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (“The Jungle Book,” “The Batman”), and costume designer Amanda Neale (“The Meg,” “What We Do in the Shadows”). Casting is by Rachel Tenner. The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (“Thor: Ragnarok,” the “LEGO®” movies). 

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Mojang Studios Production, A Jared Hess Film, “A Minecraft Movie.” The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

About MaaTri Media 

MaaTri, represents the most beautiful relationship between a mother and a daughter - Nisha Topwal & Anantya Anand aka. MyMissAnand. MaaTri is formed through a combination of two Hindi words - Maa (Mother) and PuTri (daughter) that brings forth energy, enthusiasm and determination to spread positive vibes through their outstanding content. Their content revolves around fashion, food, comedy, parenting, travel, glimpse of their family and simple day-to-day activities that both enjoy doing together. 
The duo captures a contemporary lifestyle of entrepreneur and food blogger mom and a teenage daughter and a social media influencer and shows how they both manage their work, school and personal life - simple pleasure of growing together, through engaging videos and fun visuals. Every post is curated and designed to make the audience laugh, learn, smile and entertain.

#wedding #richvsnormal  #challenge #strangerwedding  #shadi #mymissanand #missanand #anantyaanand #without #uninvitedguest

snippet.description:

https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Lyrics : 
Kora Kora Meesalatho, Kodama Kodama Adugulatho 
Kontey Kontey Chenukulatho, Kolimilanti Magatimitho Sarasara Vacchinaadu Chicchara Pidugantivaadu 
Edo Edo Thalachinaadu Evvarino Vethikinaadu 
Evaranta… Evaranta… Evarevaranta
Evaranta Evaranta Evarevarevarevaranta

Kondapalli Endi Bomma 
Kola Kallatho Chusindamma Teeyateeyani Teynelakomma
Teeyani Teraley Teesindamma
Vajrala Jilugulunna 
Rathnala Yelugulunna Kempulla Ompulunna Mohareela Merupulunna
Naa Paidi Gundeylona Edi Puttinchi 
Mariginchi Mariginchi Kariginchi Kariginchi

Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro
Kollagottinaadiro…..Kollagottinaadiro 
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Ayyayyayyo….…Aa Chinnadi 
Inkemi Chesindayyo. 
Ayyayyayyo...Aa Kurradi Aa Mantram Esindayyo..

Kannulaloni Kaatuka Megham 
Seekati Naapai Silikindey 
Maatalathoney Melikeysindi 
Marmam Edo Daasindey
Aadavaallu Manasu Adavilantidani 
Eragani Santodiva
Antha Amayakudiva
Padusupilla Teeru Pattusikkadani Pasigattalenodiva 
Votti Shontikommuva…
Letha Ennapoosava…..
Are Meesala Roshala Monaganni Pattesi 
Pasivanni Chesesi Pasaredo Poosesi…
Kollagottinaadiro
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro….
Mulleygattinaadiro…Mulleygattinaadiro…

Oopiriloni Aaviripavanaaley 
Viriviga Lekhaley Visireney
Uppena Laaga Pongey Pourushamey 
Sogasuku Sankela Veseyney
Cheekuchintha Leni Vaadi Chittam Dochavey Parahushaar Poragadni Paagal Chesavey Daaredayina Davvedayina Needayi Untaney Pereydaina Teeredayina Penimiti Antaney Addeddedde….
Kollagottinaadiro….
Kollagotti Naa Gundeyney Mulleygattinaadiro 
Kollagottinaadiro Mulleygattinaadiro…

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: The Bhootnii - Announcement | Sanjay D, Mouni R, Sunny, Palak, Nick | Sidhaant S | Deepak M | 18 Apr
snippet.description:
Get ready for a rollercoaster of horror, romance, and comedy like never before! Presenting "The Bhootnii", where love, laughter and supernatural thrills come together in the most unexpected way! 👻💘🤣

Starring the legendary Sanjay Dutt, the stunning Mouni Roy, the charming Sunny Singh, the talented Palak Tiwari, the hilarious Asif Khan, and the quirky BeYounik, this film is packed with spine-tingling moments, hilarious twists, and a whole lot of romance! 💀❤️✨

🎬The Bhootnii is set to hit theaters on 18th April 2025.

Credits : 
⭐ cast : Sanjay Dutt, Mouni Roy, Sunny Singh, Palak Tiwari, Asif Khan, BeYounik & Others
Written & Directed by : Sidhaant Sachdev
Produced by : Deepak Mukut & Sanjay Dutt
Co-Produced by : Hunar Mukut & Maanayata Dutt
Associate Producer : Johari Tailor
DOP : Santosh Thundiyil ISC
Editor : Bunty Nagi 
Screenplay & Dialogue : Vankush Arora & Sidhaant Sachdev
Production Design : Dipankar Das Gupta & Sunayana Paradkar (Teena)
Sound Design : Kunal Mehta & Parikshit Lalwani (Creative Sound Design)
BG Music :  Amar Mohile
Choreographer : Ganesh Acharya 
Executive Producer: Mehboob Ansari & Pradeep Singh
Action : Real Satish
Costume Designer- Priyanka Mundada 
Sanjay Dutt’s Costume- Anna Singh & Navin Shetty
VFX : Redifine 
VFX Supervisor - Govardhan Vigraham
Associate Director : Rishabh Rishi Kumar 
Music : ICONYK, Shabbir Ahmed, Mukund Suryawanshi (Jam8)
Creative Director : Manoj Tiwari & Rishi Anand
CEO (TDM) : Gaurav Dubey
CEO & Business Head (SRE) : Shailendra Mandowara 
Digital Mrkt. Manager (SRE) : Ajay S Singh
Production Team (SRE) : Lucky Tomar, Shivam Rao
Banner : Soham Rockstar Entertainment & Three Dimension Motion Pictures 

Watch the official Announcement now and get ready for The Bhootnii Machayegi Tandav – where the supernatural takes a hilarious turn!

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4332 - Bapuji Tapu ki Shadi Karwa ke Hi Manenge?! | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Bapuji ki Jidd | Tapu ki Shadi | Gokuldham Society | Sonu ki shadi

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: सुबह सुबह ऐसे दर्शन से आंखें तो धन्य हो गईं! 😜 Woh 7 Din - Anil Kapoor जबरदस्त Lotpot Comedy सीन
snippet.description:
वो सात दिन एक मजेदार फिल्म है जिसमें अनिल कपूर, पद्मिनी कोल्हापुरे और नसीरुद्दीन शाह की शानदार अदाकारी है। कहानी एक युवा लड़के की है जो अपने प्यार के लिए जीतोड़ मेहनत करता है। अनिल कपूर की मस्ती और पद्मिनी का दिलकश अंदाज इस फिल्म को और भी मजेदार बना देते हैं। नसीरुद्दीन शाह की हाजिरजवाबी के साथ, इस फिल्म के हास्य दृश्यों में आपको हंसी से लोटपोट कर देंगे। इसे देखना न भूलें!

Woh Saat Din is a hilarious film featuring the outstanding performances of Anil Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, and Naseeruddin Shah. The story revolves around a young man who goes to great lengths for his love. Anil Kapoor's antics and Padmini's charming presence add to the fun. With Naseeruddin Shah's wit, the comedy scenes will leave you in splits. Don't miss out on this entertaining ride!

Movie: Woh Saat Din (1983)
Cast: Anil Kapoor, Padmini Kolhapure, and Naseeruddin Shah
Director: Bapu
Music: Laxmikant–Pyarelal
Producer: Surinder Kapoor, Boney Kapoor
